{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)registerForPushNotificationsWithCompletion:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWithCompletion:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerForPushNotificationsWithCompletion:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"registerForPushNotificationsWithCompletion:"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers the device for push notifications with a completion handler."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWithCompletion:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"void (^)(NSString *, NSError *)","preciseIdentifier":"c:BFv(#*$objc(cs)NSString#*$objc(cs)NSError)","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Block called when registration completes, providing the push token or an error."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Token is nil if registration failed or user denied permission.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"completion"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method combines system permission request with Pushwoosh server registration."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"The completion handler provides feedback on both operations, allowing you to:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Update UI based on registration status"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Track registration analytics","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle errors gracefully with retry logic"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sync push token with your backend server","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle registration in onboarding flow with analytics tracking:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class OnboardingViewController: UIViewController {","","    func enableNotificationsTapped() {","        showLoadingState()","","        Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications { [weak self] token, error in","            DispatchQueue.main.async {","                self?.hideLoadingState()","","                if let error = error {","                    Analytics.track(\"push_registration_failed\", properties: [","                        \"error\": error.localizedDescription","                    ])","                    self?.showRetryOption()","                    return","                }","","                if let token = token {","                    Analytics.track(\"push_registration_success\")","                    self?.syncTokenWithBackend(token)","                    self?.proceedToNextStep()","                } else {","                    Analytics.track(\"push_permission_denied\")","                    self?.showPermissionDeniedInfo()","                }","            }","        }","    }","","    private func syncTokenWithBackend(_ token: String) {","        APIClient.shared.updatePushToken(token) { result in","            if case .failure(let error) = result {","                Logger.error(\"Backend sync failed: \\(error)\")","            }","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/